<HL>
   Voplex to Sell Line to Sonoco
</HL>
<DATE>
04/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   VOT SONO
</CO>
<IN>
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   TROY, Mich. -- Sonoco Products Co. of Hartsville, S.C.,
signed a letter of intent to purchase Voplex Products Co.'s
plastic cartridge business, the two companies said.
   Terms weren't disclosed.
</LP>
<TEXT>
   Included in the sale would be Voplex's manufacturing and
sales operation in Canandaigua, N.Y., which produces and
markets cartridges for the packaging industry.
   Voplex designs, engineers and manufactures decorative trim
components for the automotive industry.
</TEXT>
